YOLOv8n Vessel Detection Model Evaluation (test data)

Generates predictions from test images to evaluate the 3 models trained on the generated datasets single-pol-2ch (baseline), single-pol-3ch and dula-pol-3ch.

In[9]:
# Run validation with Ultralytics
test_results = model.val(
    data=yaml_path,
    project=eval_path,
    split='test',
    conf=0.01,       # minimum confidence threshold for detections
    save_txt=True,    # saves detection results one file per image
    iou=0.65,          # Default IoU threshold for NMS
    plots=False,
    verbose=True
)
